'''2013年委内瑞拉总统选举'''是一个临时总统选举，这是由于2013年3月5日前委内瑞拉总统[[烏戈·查維茲|烏戈·查維茲]]因病逝世，而提前于2013年4月14日举行的全国总统大选。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-21731336 Venezuela announces post-Chavez election date] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-21731336 |date=20190910035644 }} BBC, 9 March 2013</ref>马杜罗胜出成功当选下一届总统。

==背景==
查韦斯在[[2012年委内瑞拉总统选举|2012年委内瑞拉总统选举]]获胜之后，前往[[古巴|古巴]]进行癌症治疗，后返回国内部队医院继续进行治疗。1月10日前后，由于查韦斯因病未能及时进行总统就职典礼，查韦斯的竞选对手呼吁进行重新选举。<ref>[http://www.kjrh.com/dpp/news/world/venezuelan-president-hugo-chavez-is-deadaccording-to-countrys-vice-president Venezuelan President Hugo Chavez is dead, according to country's vice president] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20130411054901/http://www.kjrh.com/dpp/news/world/venezuelan-president-hugo-chavez-is-deadaccording-to-countrys-vice-president |date=2013-04-11 }} AP, 5 March 2013</ref><ref>[http://www.cortezjournal.com/article/20130304/API/1303041031/Venezuela:-Chavez's-respiratory-problems-worsens Venezuela: Chavez very delicate with new infection] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cortezjournal.com/article/20130304/API/1303041031/Venezuela:-Chavez's-respiratory-problems-worsens |date=20160328203751 }} Cortez Journal, 4 March 2013</ref>

